name: TotemZ - The Owl
description: TotemZ animal spirit #7 - The Owl ! The owl, or night eagle, is above all a spiritual animal. Endowed with exceptional vision almost a hundred times better than human's, the owl is associated with clairvoyance. Able to see what others do not see day or night, its symbolism is strong in the expression of truth. So it is the wisdom, knowledge and informed decision making that hide behind the owl.
